{"tid":2361014,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"好驚唱國歌唱到走哂音","createTime":"2021-01-10T09:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T10:15:16.000Z","uid":141267,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1f9f09c1269afca27e8adca07be474c47043fb6c","tid":2361014,"uid":141267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T09:53:25.000Z","msg":"話說我本行係古典音樂，我都好鍾意首願榮光歸香港，次次唱都感動到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但每次聽都硬係覺得原本個版本有少少奇怪<br />\n因為佢頭尾段都係4句，一共8小節<br />\n但中段又短左，少左一句<br />\n個感覺唔係好平衡，尤其我地慣左留意個form，就覺得作為一首國歌總係爭緊D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再加埋個原key 都比較難唱，咁我就諗左一個小小既改動，想問下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就整左兩個版本<br />\n一個用原本既Key - C major 開始<br />\n中間加多一句，然後轉key 做F major<br />\n呢個版本好處係後面冇咁高音<br />\n但都有D問題就係中間果段變左好低音 (去到E)<br />\n男聲好易冇晒聲，女聲就問題不大<br />\n去片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PjEoa8uea28&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPjEoa8uea28%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7RmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=aa5d2854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PjEoa8uea28&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個版本係由F major 開始<br />\n中間冇左個轉調，咁就由頭到尾都係F major<br />\n呢個Key 應該好唱好多<br />\n (不過中段係會突然低左落去，係有D 奇怪但如果要顧及個key 容易唱，就真係冇咩其他辦法)<br />\n去片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bmph-yQZXSw&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBmph-yQZXSw%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7RmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=c88c8517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Bmph-yQZXSw&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以俾下意見，如果大家鍾意既，搵人填返中間果句歌詞，就係一個易唱D既版本啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：代朋友po，各位ching有問題我會搵返佢答。佢人係外國有時差，會覆得慢啲"},{"pid":"da8fb0ac5c7f91df5b563fb55e1c4a88512d3189","tid":2361014,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n利申: 音樂痴"},{"pid":"556099f8bf7dc494f9bdb13fe17013dac5e535e8","tid":2361014,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T10:00:10.000Z","msg":"其實原版應該無人可以原key原調唱晒成首 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定某個位升/降8度"},{"pid":"32e2b29256a0a1873c7855e32554506e7c25c973","tid":2361014,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f9f09c1269afca27e8adca07be474c47043fb6c","tid":2361014,"uid":141267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T09:53:25.000Z","msg":"話說我本行係古典音樂，我都好鍾意首願榮光歸香港，次次唱都感動到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但每次聽都硬係覺得原本個版本有少少奇怪<br />\n因為佢頭尾段都係4句，一共8小節<br />\n但中段又短左，少左一句<br />\n個感覺唔係好平衡，尤其我地慣左留意個form，就覺得作為一首國歌總係爭緊D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再加埋個原key 都比較難唱，咁我就諗左一個小小既改動，想問下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我就整左兩個版本<br />\n一個用原本既Key - C major 開始<br />\n中間加多一句，然後轉key 做F major<br />\n呢個版本好處係後面冇咁高音<br />\n但都有D問題就係中間果段變左好低音 (去到E)<br />\n男聲好易冇晒聲，女聲就問題不大<br />\n去片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PjEoa8uea28&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPjEoa8uea28%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7RmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=aa5d2854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PjEoa8uea2